aha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91832c6b8b99bd8dff504d287766a156dda68289","tid":1431322,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"但示威者提出新的不合理的訴求<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查都不合理？<br />\n普選都不合理？"},{"pid":"10832f5745b5929e0f1878c60a4e605d8077b1ec","tid":1431322,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3f8b9af84fc9a63a552b43326409bba362be52","tid":1431322,"uid":11365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:26:19.000Z","msg":"仲停留係有法必依 講乜撚野法治社會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"佢同廢老講架"},{"pid":"6a98454669d67b8c972daf0aa84e45b7f25c1cfe","tid":1431322,"uid":230036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"係政府教識香港人 和平沒有用"},{"pid":"62f19ca6c54ddb7d7a913212d5dec408363fa912","tid":1431322,"uid":264992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"咁都俾你發現到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21067007aef5b9cdab7fcc6b04f1fa5bd58450b","tid":1431322,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"咁唔搞亂香港 我地去搞亂中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6ffae835431ce93f24be0e25b6cd46d56f381a","tid":1431322,"uid":174815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/as